data.text:
1618-1677 Roger Burgoyne 2nd Baronet, MP. Son of Sir John Burgoyne 1st Baronet pf Sutton & Wroxall d1657 and Jane daughter of Julius Kempe of Spains Hall, Finchingfield

Knighted in 1641 he took a prominent part inthe Civil War upon the side of Charles l and was in exile abroad when he succeeded to his father's title and estates here and at Wroxall. He returned in 1661 and was made High Sheriff of Bedfordshire in 1661 Great friend of Ralph Verney www.flickr.com/photos/52219527@N00/3597246327/ who he warned that the Parliament troops were about to raid his home Claydon House, Buckinghamshire,. Sir Ralph fled to France but returned after several years

He m1 Anne d1658 daughter of Charles Snelling, London merchant

1. John dc1647

2. Jane m John Symonds 1666 of Honiley / Yeldham widower of Elizabeth Quarles www.flickr.com/photos/52219527@N00/14341611139/

3. John 1651-1709 3 Bart www.flickr.com/photos/52219527@N00/7266968564/

4 Anne m Sir John Raymond of essex gent

5. Mary d1677 m William Guyon of essex gent

6. Judith m Robert Pigott.

7. Elizabeth d1677.

He m2 1660 Anne daughter of John Robinson of Deighton, Yorks
